Tavatron:

Tavatron caught Vehement's blast in her left side, the force alone sending 
her flying several meters back. Her left shoulder plate sizzled and her side 
armor was burned and melded to her circuitry. Tavatron growled and fired 
another sicle shaped energy blast at Vehement. She made it a point to charge 
this one so as to inflict more damage than the previous two.

CF:

The base shook from the force of the Brotherhood's attacks.
